Background (GUI item property)
==============================

Sets the background of an item. This can be an image in .[TGA](TGA\_(file\_format)) format (a reference to the filename, without extension, with the path relative do the game installation directory) or a reference to a material on a material list (use the shader path/name as defined in the .[MTR](MTR\_(file\_format)) file).

Syntax
------

`background `*`material`*

Default value
-------------

`""`

Example(s)
----------

`background "gui/assets/scanlines"`


